"reviewcomment":"Max City is AMAZING! Jason and his team catered our October 2013 wedding in Pasadena and we can&#39;t say enough about their food and their service. We talked to them last year when we started planning the big day and they were quick to respond to all inquires, professional and even found another wedding in the area where we could stop by undetected, behind the scenes, to test everything out. We knew right away we&#39;d found our the right guys. <br><br>For the wedding we went with brisket, ribs and bbq chicken. Sides included cornbread, mac n cheese, baked beans and cucumber salad. We also asked Max City to cater at the cocktail hour. We went with the bacon wrapped dates, grilled cheese with mini pickle and a german dish Jason helped design of sausage and sauerkraut (to go with our German biergarten theme). We got SO many compliments on all of the food. We were initially worried our vegetarian guests might have a hard time finding something on our meat-centered menu, but we also got nothing but praise from them- one of them even going to say that the sides at our wedding were better than any vegetarian dish they&#39;d been served at any prior weddings. Our guests went back for seconds and some thirds! The food was THAT good! <br><br>We would recommend Max City to anyone and now can&#39;t wait for them to open up their restaurant!",
