"ogimage":"http://s3-media3.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/WdpCAF_ZF_eujqaFzC7fJg/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.5",
"reviewcomment":"Ohhhh Mexico!  The Taoc&#39;s here are off the hook DEEEELISH!  <br><br>I&#39;ve had this place bookmarked forever and was so happy to have finally been able to get my taco&#39;s on finally!<br><br>Its not a particularly big place but there is a good number of tables to sit down to enjoy the yummy goodness!  Since it was my first time here I opted for the sampler that consists of 6 mini tacos of their top 6 tacos listed on the huge blackboard that list all that they offer.  They do allow you to switch out with others with the exception of a few like the pescado and camarones.<br><br>Sampler ~ <a href='http://www.yelp.com/biz_photos/guisados-los-angeles?select=HSYA1OE5V5LFPQ3JOEQkVw#HLvbgoggHaKOskjvsxNctg'>yelp.com/biz_photos/guis…</a> For $6.95 this is the best deal ever.  I had the Steak Picado, Bistek en Salsa Rojo, Tinga, Mole Poblano, Chicharron and Chuleta.  These tacos are not really big.  They are about the size of your palm and can be eaten in 2 bites.  All of them were really good.  However out of all of them I really enjoyed the Tinga with the flavorful sauce. The chicharron threw me off as I was expecting the crunchy ones but here they have it smothered in a sauce.  Although it was not crunchy it had a good flavor.  The tortilla here is thicker than what you typical get.  I think since most of their tacos are more sauce based it requires a thicker tortilla to hold it.<br><br>Chorizo ~ <a href='http://www.yelp.com/biz_photos/guisados-los-angeles?select=HSYA1OE5V5LFPQ3JOEQkVw#AppH9qgzKNEJmPV4ogS2Kg'>yelp.com/biz_photos/guis…</a> After having a small piece of a friends chorizo I had to order one for myself.  As stuffed as I was I really enjoyed this taco and would definitely be one that I order next time.<br><br>The one thing that would have taken my first Guisado experience up even more would have been a cold glass of michelada.  But I really enjoyed the melon aguas fresca.<br><br>Eyes ~ Oh my which 6 do I start with!<br>Nose ~ I  smell goodness!<br>Ear ~ Lots of happy people eating.<br>Mouth ~ Oh Man why did I wait so long to get here!<br>Tummy ~ So stuffed and satisfied!",
