"ogimage":"http://s3-media2.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/pnbT-hn_k4njE1gPofxYzg/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.5",
"reviewcomment":"What can I say? I love this place! JC and his cousin are awesome. Since this is a small place, I&#39;ve never had to wait any length of time for my food. And that counts a lot when u only have a set time for lunch at work.. We all know each other by name now after the few times I have visited- it feels like home. Where else can I go for lunch by myself and actually have an on-going conversation with the owner and chef? No where else but JC&#39;s.. <br><br>I don&#39;t leave many reviews for any businesses- but when they are deserved, I have to take the time to show my appreciation. Well, actually, my big belly&#39;s appreciation. :) <br><br>I ordered the pulled pork sandwich with fries today- not my first time trying it, and definitely not going to be the last. Its served on a hamburger bun and loaded with a great portion of awesome and tender pulled pork tossed in BBQ.. I say tossed cuz I was watching JC cook my meal and sure enough, he tossed that juicy pork all up in that BBQ sauce. MMMM! lol. I&#39;ve been to other places where their pulled pork sandwich is their specialty and is known to be &#34;the best around&#34; and these other restaurants never live up to that claim. But JC certainly knows what he is doing- the pork is juicy and soft and the sauce is damn tasty.. It&#39;s NOT one of those pulled pork sandwiches that fall apart and get all over the place cuz whoever made it drenched it in sauce to cover up poor pork quality- JC&#39;s pulled pork is perfectly sauced and perfectly proportioned in my book. <br><br>Next to this delicious sandwich is a HEAP of fries. I&#39;m a big fan of fries. And these fries DON&#39;T disappoint at all. The seasoning JC uses is  like a Lawry&#39;s seasoning salt, but wayyyyy better! <br><br>If I have the time at work tomorrow, I&#39;ll be stopping in again to try one of their Mexican dishes.. I hear their Asada is fantastic.<br><br>Final thought: <br>I can taste the LOVE in every single bite- JC and the crew know what&#39;s up when it comes to preparing awesome meals!",
