"rating":"4.5",
"reviewcomment":"Two dishes ... Dino&#39;s Famous Chicken, which is the ultimate flavored grilled chicken that you will ever have.  The chicken comes to you in this bright orange color.  It&#39;s been marinating for who knows how long to get that flavor and color soaked into the meat.  But once you get it, you will want more.  We&#39;ve had it before with just the chicken with all the sauce and spices on top.  I would recommend getting it that way versus getting it over fries.  We got it over fries before and the fries soak up all the juices which sounds good when you think about it but it wasn&#39;t that good in my opinion.  It&#39;s better ripping up that juicy sweet chicken meat and dipping it into the juices.  So YUMMY! <br><br>Another dish there that will probably clog all your arteries but is worth trying is their DUI Fries.  It&#39;s Pastrami and Carne Asade Chili Cheese Fries.  It&#39;s a heart attack waiting to happen but it&#39;s so just GOOD!  It comes in a huge serving and we had to bring home extras sharing between three people!  But you know what, it&#39;s even better the next day warmed up in your microwave.  <br><br>They also have orange bang which is always delicious!  <br><br>The place itself is definitely a hole in the wall.  Dirty floors and tables.  Don&#39;t expect it to be clean but hey, if you want good food for cheap, you have to sacrifice some luxuries.  Parking can be bad too but it&#39;s such a good place for some cheap good food and I can see why it would be packed especially at night.  It&#39;s good drunk food.",
